---
// "What I'm Building" section — featured projects
---

<section aria-labelledby="building-heading" class="space-y-8">
    <!-- Section label -->
    <div>
      <span class="inline-block border border-base-content/40 text-base-content/80 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest rounded-full px-3 py-1">
        What I&apos;m Building
      </span>
    </div>

    <!-- MyAbem at ABEM -->
    <div class="bg-base-200 text-base-content rounded-box px-8 py-10 space-y-5">
      <h2 id="building-heading" class="text-3xl font-bold">MyAbem</h2>
      <p class="text-base-content/70 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide">
        Project Lead &mdash; American Board of Emergency Medicine
      </p>

      <p class="text-base-content/90 leading-relaxed text-lg">
        The <strong class="text-base-content font-semibold">American Board of Emergency Medicine (ABEM)</strong>
        certifies emergency physicians who meet its educational, professional standing, and examination
        standards &mdash; ensuring the highest standards in the specialty of Emergency Medicine.
        ABEM holds the interests of patients and their families in the highest standing, particularly
        with regard to the safest and highest-quality emergency care.
      </p>

      <p class="text-base-content/80 leading-relaxed">
        <strong class="text-base-content font-semibold">MyAbem</strong> is the physician-facing
        portal that board-certified emergency physicians rely on to manage their certification,
        continuing education, and professional credentials. It&apos;s the digital backbone connecting
        ABEM to the physicians it certifies across the country.
      </p>

      <p class="text-base-content/80 leading-relaxed">
        I&apos;m leading the MyAbem development team through a transformation to
        <strong class="text-base-content font-semibold">multi-agent AI workflows</strong> &mdash;
        applying the same engineering principles I explore across all my work to modernize how
        the team builds and ships software.
      </p>

      <div class="pt-2">
        <a
          href="https://www.abem.org"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="btn btn-sm border-base-content/60 text-base-content bg-transparent hover:bg-base-content/15 hover:border-base-content"
        >
          Visit ABEM
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M18 13v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6"/>
            <polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"/>
            <line x1="10" y1="14" x2="21" y2="3"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Lessi AI -->
    <div class="bg-base-200 text-base-content rounded-box px-8 py-10 space-y-5">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold">Lessi AI</h2>
      <p class="text-base-content/70 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide">
        Co-Founder &amp; CTO
      </p>

      <p class="text-base-content/90 leading-relaxed text-lg">
        <strong class="text-base-content font-semibold">Lessi</strong> is an AI platform designed
        to help <strong class="text-base-content font-semibold">special education teachers</strong>
        create high-quality instructional materials tailored to the needs of every student.
      </p>

      <p class="text-base-content/80 leading-relaxed">
        The platform uses AI to generate and adapt lesson plans, assessments, reading passages,
        and instructional supports &mdash; all aligned with students&apos; IEPs, state and national
        standards, and evidence-based instructional practices.
      </p>

      <p class="text-base-content/80 leading-relaxed">
        Lessi combines AI generation, structured educational content, and teacher workflows to
        dramatically reduce preparation time while improving instruction quality.
      </p>

      <div class="pt-2">
        <a
          href="https://www.lessi.ai"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="btn btn-sm border-base-content/60 text-base-content bg-transparent hover:bg-base-content/15 hover:border-base-content"
        >
          Visit Lessi AI
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M18 13v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6"/>
            <polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"/>
            <line x1="10" y1="14" x2="21" y2="3"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
</section>
